1Maleka wosɔhi woŋ hoŋe kuthuthu nama koŋ. Kɛna kute yaŋ sosa ŋɔta kafay woŋ ka ŋaye ka kuthahinɛ koŋ, e ndɛ dunkuno saapa hu pɛthi biyo hu ka tha kuyɛkɛŋ koŋ mankande ka haŋ. 2Wundɛ pɛthi biyo hu ka tha kuyɛkɛŋ koŋ mankande ka, awa kɛna fuŋ hiti hu thɔyande iŋ hiti hu ka buu bumandiŋ. Huŋ fuŋ haaŋ kaŋ woŋ mɛnɛ kufenaŋ koŋ niyɔ huntuma nagbi iŋ hiti hu fuŋɛ ka pɛthi wundɛ ka haŋ. 3Awa ŋaye ka hiti haŋ haŋ baŋ, sisiŋ bohe kɛndɛ fuŋa e bindɛ kɔ ŋɔta kafay ka. Bindɛ dunkuno nde sɛmbɛ nɔŋ sɛmbɛ ba k
