dɔma, na “Bateeti woŋ.” 12Nkinikiniŋ kimayoŋ kiŋ daŋande; awa naa daŋande kiŋ na, wuŋ pɛyɛ hɛlɛŋ nkinikinini kiye ba niyɔ. 13Maleka wosɔŋ-wunthe woŋ hoŋe kuthuthu nama koŋ. Kɛna yuye yaŋ thampa tha si fuŋ ŋaye ka ŋaasɛ ŋaŋanaŋ ŋa ka thadoŋ tha ka thebulu woboy wo fuŋune saraka ka Masaala wo kɔɔyɛ ka kɔtɔkɔy kɛnama woŋ. 14Thampa thaŋ dome ka maleka wosɔŋ-wunthe woŋ, na “Pɛɛka malekɛŋ bibinaŋ bi yuko nde beŋ ka mankɔ mamandiŋ ma dɔma maŋ na mankɔ ma ka Yufiretisi maŋ!” 15Malekɛŋ bibinaŋ beŋ peeko;
